{"tid":1395974,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府內部白色恐怖，但請各公務員要繼續堅持，人夠多就無事","createTime":"2019-08-02T02:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:25:09.000Z","uid":16142,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b74156c10631beeffe78a106eab847a2057c8b50","tid":1395974,"uid":16142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"做緊某政府部門，白色恐怖好嚴重，而家已經吹晒風話8月5號會record返工情況<br />\n上司講明會針對以下情況<br />\n1. 集體拎VL嘅人<br />\n2. 集體拎Sick Leave嘅人<br />\n3. 礦工嘅人<br />\n4. 有返工但唔做嘢嘅人<br />\n屌你老母仲話會有高層嚟睇大家返工嘅情況，叫大家執正啲，準時返工唔好玩手機<br />\n仆街，玩擇名<br />\n利申：一早請咗幾日VL，希望唔會俾人秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家都可以堅持，人夠多就無事"},{"pid":"ee0d5b9dfb5bd0003d6f12036d234d888deb2f65","tid":1395974,"uid":247090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"樓主請幾日VL咁堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0ec40d915f30c9a6184e97be5502e88102549d","tid":1395974,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}